{"tid":722810,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"8強有機會免費看美斯鬥C朗","createTime":"2018-06-30T00:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T06:58:39.000Z","uid":36494,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"425656abd6b2c832888672ed8b893f2447538464","tid":722810,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T00:21:25.000Z","msg":"ViuTV世界盃前公布，會直播香港時間7月6日（星期五）晚10時的8強比賽，這場會由法國、阿根廷的勝方對烏拉圭、葡萄牙的勝方。如果阿根廷及葡萄牙在16強皆能贏波的話，香港球迷可以從免費直播見到兩隊在8強對決。ViuTV還會免費直播瑞士與瑞典勝方對英格蘭與哥倫比亞勝方的8強。如果英格蘭爭氣贏多場，球迷就可以免費看到他們踢8強。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wc2018.hk01.com/article/204558/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83-viutv%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E5%85%A9%E5%A0%B416%E5%BC%B7-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%94%94%E7%88%AD%E6%B0%A3%E6%90%9E%E5%88%B0%E6%92%AD%E6%82%B6%E6%B3%A2?utm_source=fbpost+sports&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_campaign=WorldCup2018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwc2018.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F204558%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%259B%2583-viutv%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25A0%25B416%25E5%25BC%25B7-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2594%2594%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%2590%259E%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2592%25AD%25E6%2582%25B6%25E6%25B3%25A2%3Futm_source%3Dfbpost%2Bsports%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_campaign%3DWorldCup2018&d=xYDnsYMJANfNLmNsctYieRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8dd253f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wc2018.hk01.com/article/204558/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9B%83-viutv%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E5%85%A9%E5%A0%B416%E5%BC%B7-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%94%94%E7%88%AD%E6%B0%A3%E6%90%9E%E5%88%B0%E6%92%AD%E6%82%B6%E6%B3%A2?utm_source=fbpost+sports&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_campaign=WorldCup2018</a>"},{"pid":"392bd201cbb618935554dc1dbd11915e59786619","tid":722810,"uid":55,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T00:24:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64650958ffc08143837b4d3a08bddb4ec379fb3e","tid":722810,"uid":171754,"